{"tid":1768132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修馬會？","createTime":"2019-12-04T00:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T06:26:37.000Z","uid":41157,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"855c442b63efd7916ba6c53e0700423dab37d683","tid":1768132,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T00:58:43.000Z","msg":"其實運動發生半年<br />\n馬會試過取消賽事，更改開場時間，數唔到咁多次提早關投注站<br />\n對佢收入實有影響<br />\n但馬會半年嚟有冇話過示威者半句？<br />\n係一次都冇，就算連國慶賽馬日都取消哂所有擦鞋嘢<br />\n盡量低調完成<br />\n我覺得馬會喺保持政治中立呢方面已經做得好好 <br />\n所以唔好搞佢啦"},{"pid":"c96d9fe899d103f9f742693e6dc162c138b5b24c","tid":1768132,"uid":41157,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:01:48.000Z","msg":"講漏左<br />\n今晚係國際騎師賽<br />\n星期日係國際賽事<br />\n可以話全球馬壇本星期會聚焦香港<br />\n舉下banner都還好，如果大肆破壞設施，嚇親外訪嘅馬同來賓就絕對唔好囉"},{"pid":"562e59992e60958e72d9e6e67e2ae33d32b2fbdf","tid":1768132,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:02:34.000Z","msg":"無怨無仇，唔好搞。搞中字頭好過"},{"pid":"9c4cf93adfe3390648f2e004d62e7b8a2c4d5147","tid":1768132,"uid":14458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:05:37.000Z","msg":"可以同大家講 馬會有條team專做網上打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家自己睇返出面幾多人撑馬會就知"},{"pid":"d6c4f5d2c384cf726d98c0d459cead19c864aba9","tid":1768132,"uid":46241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T01:29:36.000Z","msg":"唔搞咪on9 <br />\n搞黎有乜實際作用 <br />\n暖氣軍師咪叫手捉送頭<br />\n咪比五毛吹風<br />\n咁得閒幫手文宣8/12啦"},{"pid":"68369b05a48327cd0aac963a6963dd4d89493679","tid":1768132,"uid":150363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T06:21:59.000Z","msg":"係就黎裝修啦<br />\n想射波 唔想返工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af27e5fda2ebe1b3092f275cb28e24b076c7ca93","tid":1768132,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68369b05a48327cd0aac963a6963dd4d89493679","tid":1768132,"uid":150363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi